   "source": [
    "# 05 - 人工校正与迭代优化\n",
    "\n",
    "**目标**: 实现 Human-in-the-Loop 流程, 找出模型不确定的样本, 人工标注, 重新训练。\n",
    "\n",
    "这是整个项目中最接近"实际科研"的环节——在天文学中, 专业天文学家就是这样与 AI 协作发现新天体的。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import sys\n",
    "sys.path.insert(0, \"..\")\n",
    "\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import pandas as pd\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "import seaborn as sns\n",
    "import pickle\n",
    "import joblib\n",
    "from sklearn.metrics import accuracy_score, f1_score, classification_report\n",
    "from IPython.display import display, clear_output\n",
    "import ipywidgets as widgets\n",
    "\n",
    "sns.set_style(\"whitegrid\")\n",
    "%matplotlib inline"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 1. 加载模型和数据"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "from src.data.preprocess import CLASS_NAMES\n",
    "from src.review.annotator import find_uncertain_samples, merge_reviewed_labels, review_summary\n",
    "\n",
    "# 加载数据\n",
    "test = np.load(\"../data/processed/test.npz\")\n",
    "X_test, y_test = test[\"X\"], test[\"y\"]\n",
    "\n",
    "with open(\"../data/processed/label_encoder.pkl\", \"rb\") as f:\n",
    "    label_encoder = pickle.load(f)\n",
    "\n",
    "# 加载 XGBoost 模型\n",
    "model = joblib.load(\"../models/xgboost_baseline.pkl\")\n",
    "print(f\"模型已加载, 测试集: {X_test.shape}\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 2. 找出模型不确定的样本"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 找置信度最低的 30 个样本\n",
    "uncertain = find_uncertain_samples(\n",
    "    model, X_test, y_test,\n",
    "    confidence_threshold=0.6,\n",
    "    max_samples=30\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"找到 {len(uncertain)} 个低置信度样本\")\n",
    "print(f\"置信度范围: [{uncertain['confidence'].min():.3f}, {uncertain['confidence'].max():.3f}]\")\n",
    "uncertain.head(10)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 统计: 模型在哪些类别上最不确定?\n",
    "fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(10, 5))\n",
    "uncertain[\"true_name\"] = uncertain[\"true_label\"].map(\n",
    "    lambda x: CLASS_NAMES.get(label_encoder.classes_[x], str(x))[:25]\n",
    ")\n",
    "uncertain[\"true_name\"].value_counts().plot(kind=\"barh\", ax=ax, color=\"coral\")\n",
    "ax.set_xlabel(\"Number of uncertain samples\")\n",
    "ax.set_title(\"低置信度样本的真实类别分布\")\n",
    "plt.tight_layout()\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 3. 人工标注界面\n",
    "\n",
    "逐条查看低置信度样本, 人工判断其正确类别。\n",
    "\n",
    "在实际项目中, 你会看光变曲线图来判断。这里我们用一个简洁的交互式工具。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "from src.utils.visualization import plot_light_curve\n",
    "from src.data.download import load_plasticc\n",
    "from src.data.preprocess import extract_lightcurve_by_object\n",
    "\n",
    "# 加载原始数据用于绘制光变曲线\n",
    "train_df, _, meta = load_plasticc(\"../data/raw/plasticc\")\n",
    "\n",
    "# 构建索引映射: 测试集 index -> object_id\n",
    "# (在实际使用中, 你需要保存这个映射)\n",
    "\n",
    "def show_sample_for_review(sample_idx: int):\n",
    "    \"\"\"展示待复核样本的光变曲线\"\"\"\n",
    "    # 这里展示不确定样本的情况\n",
    "    row = uncertain.iloc[sample_idx]\n",
    "    prob = model.predict_proba(X_test[row[\"index\"]:row[\"index\"]+1])[0]\n",
    "    top3_idx = np.argsort(prob)[::-1][:3]\n",
    "\n",
    "    print(f\"样本 #{sample_idx} (test index={row['index']})\")\n",
    "    print(f\"真实标签: {CLASS_NAMES.get(label_encoder.classes_[row['true_label']], '?')}\")\n",
    "    print(f\"模型预测: {CLASS_NAMES.get(label_encoder.classes_[row['predicted']], '?')}\")\n",
    "    print(f\"置信度: {row['confidence']:.3f}\")\n",
    "    print(\"\\nTop-3 预测:\")\n",
    "    for i, idx in enumerate(top3_idx):\n",
    "        cls_id = label_encoder.classes_[idx]\n",
    "        name = CLASS_NAMES.get(cls_id, str(cls_id))\n",
    "        print(f\"  {i+1}. {name:40s} prob={prob[idx]:.3f}\")\n",
    "\n",
    "    print(f\"\\n你的判断: (选择 1-{len(label_encoder.classes_)} 或输入类名)\")\n",
    "\n",
    "# 测试\n",
    "show_sample_for_review(0)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 4. 批量人工校正\n",
    "\n",
    "对不确定样本做出判断后, 更新标签并重新评估。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 模拟: 假设我们对不确定样本做了人工判断\n",
    "# 在实际使用中, 你会用上面的标注界面逐条判断\n",
    "# 这里用模型的 Top-1 预测作为"人工判断"的模拟\n",
    "\n",
    "# 模拟人工校正: 对置信度 > 0.5 的样本, 采用模型预测; 否则保持原标签\n",
    "reviewed_indices = uncertain[\"index\"].values\n",
    "corrected_labels = np.where(\n",
    "    uncertain[\"confidence\"].values > 0.5,\n",
    "    uncertain[\"predicted\"].values,  # 高置信度: 采用模型预测\n",
    "    uncertain[\"true_label\"].values   # 低置信度: 保持原标签\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "# 合并校正后的标签\n",
    "y_updated = merge_reviewed_labels(y_test, reviewed_indices, corrected_labels)\n",
    "\n",
    "# 统计改动\n",
    "summary = review_summary(y_test, y_updated)\n",
    "print(f\"总样本数: {summary['total_samples']}\")\n",
    "print(f\"修改标签: {summary['changed_labels']}\")\n",
    "print(f\"修改比例: {summary['change_rate']:.2%}\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 5. Active Learning 迭代循环\n",
    "\n",
    "完整的人机协作流程:"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def active_learning_round(\n",
    "    model,\n",
    "    X_train, y_train,  # 已标注的训练集\n",
    "    X_pool, y_pool,    # 未标注/待审核池\n",
    "    n_samples: int = 50,\n",
    "    confidence_threshold: float = 0.6,\n",
    ") -> dict:\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    单轮 Active Learning:\n",
    "    1. 在池中找出模型最不确定的样本\n",
    "    2. (人工标注后) 将校正后的样本加入训练集\n",
    "    3. 重新训练模型\n",
    "    4. 返回性能变化\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    # 步骤 1: 找不确定样本\n",
    "    uncertain = find_uncertain_samples(\n",
    "        model, X_pool, y_pool,\n",
    "        confidence_threshold=confidence_threshold,\n",
    "        max_samples=n_samples,\n",
    "    )\n",
    "\n",
    "    # 步骤 2: 模拟人工标注 (实际中由你来做)\n",
    "    # 这里用真实标签模拟\"专家判断\"\n",
    "    reviewed_indices = uncertain[\"index\"].values\n",
    "    corrected_labels = uncertain[\"true_label\"].values  # 专家给了正确标签\n",
    "\n",
    "    # 步骤 3: 扩充训练集\n",
    "    X_new = np.concatenate([X_train, X_pool[reviewed_indices]])\n",
    "    y_new = np.concatenate([y_train, corrected_labels])\n",
    "\n",
    "    # 从池中移除已标注样本\n",
    "    remaining_mask = np.ones(len(X_pool), dtype=bool)\n",
    "    remaining_mask[reviewed_indices] = False\n",
    "    X_pool_remaining = X_pool[remaining_mask]\n",
    "    y_pool_remaining = y_pool[remaining_mask]\n",
    "\n",
    "    # 步骤 4: 重新训练\n",
    "    from src.models.baseline import train_xgboost_baseline\n",
    "    new_model = train_xgboost_baseline(\n",
    "        X_new, y_new,\n",
    "        X_test, y_test,\n",
    "        num_classes=len(np.unique(y_new)),\n",
    "    )\n",
    "\n",
    "    # 评估\n",
    "    y_pred_before = model.predict(X_test)\n",
    "    y_pred_after = new_model.predict(X_test)\n",
    "\n",
    "    metrics = {\n",
    "        \"train_size_before\": len(X_train),\n",
    "        \"train_size_after\": len(X_new),\n",
    "        \"pool_size_after\": len(X_pool_remaining),\n",
    "        \"acc_before\": accuracy_score(y_test, y_pred_before),\n",
    "        \"acc_after\": accuracy_score(y_test, y_pred_after),\n",
    "        \"f1_before\": f1_score(y_test, y_pred_before, average=\"macro\"),\n",
    "        \"f1_after\": f1_score(y_test, y_pred_after, average=\"macro\"),\n",
    "    }\n",
    "\n",
    "    return metrics, new_model, X_new, y_new, X_pool_remaining, y_pool_remaining\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"Active Learning 函数已定义。\")\n",
    "print(\"使用方式: metrics, new_model, X_train, y_train, X_pool, y_pool = active_learning_round(...)\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 运行 3 轮 Active Learning, 观察性能变化\n",
    "val = np.load(\"../data/processed/val.npz\")\n",
    "X_val, y_val = val[\"X\"], val[\"y\"]\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"\\nActive Learning 模拟 (3 轮):\")\n",
    "print(f\"{'轮次':>4}  {'训练集大小':>10}  {'Acc Before':>10}  {'Acc After':>10}  {'F1 Before':>10}  {'F1 After':>10}\")\n",
    "print(\"-\" * 70)\n",
    "\n",
    "current_model = model\n",
    "X_train_cur, y_train_cur = X_val.copy(), y_val.copy()\n",
    "X_pool_cur, y_pool_cur = np.load(\"../data/processed/train.npz\")[\"X\"], np.load(\"../data/processed/train.npz\")[\"y\"]\n",
    "\n",
    "for round_num in range(1, 4):\n",
    "    metrics, current_model, X_train_cur, y_train_cur, X_pool_cur, y_pool_cur = \\\n",
    "        active_learning_round(\n",
    "            current_model,\n",
    "            X_train_cur, y_train_cur,\n",
    "            X_pool_cur, y_pool_cur,\n",
    "            n_samples=50,\n",
    "            confidence_threshold=0.6\n",
    "        )\n",
    "\n",
    "    print(\n",
    "        f\"{round_num:4d}  {metrics['train_size_after']:10d}  \"\n",
    "        f\"{metrics['acc_before']:10.4f}  {metrics['acc_after']:10.4f}  \"\n",
    "        f\"{metrics['f1_before']:10.4f}  {metrics['f1_after']:10.4f}\"\n",
    "    )"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 保存最终优化后的模型\n",
    "joblib.dump(current_model, \"../models/xgboost_optimized.pkl\")\n",
    "print(\"优化后的模型已保存到 ../models/xgboost_optimized.pkl\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 6. 总结\n",
    "\n",
    "通过以上 5 个 Notebook, 你完成了:\n",
    "\n",
    "1. **数据探索**: 理解 PLAsTiCC 数据结构和不同天体的光变曲线特征\n",
    "2. **特征工程**: 提取 20+ 统计特征, 构建标准化训练集\n",
    "3. **XGBoost 基线**: 快速建立性能参考 (~75-85% 准确率)\n",
    "4. **LSTM 深度学习**: 直接从序列学习, 与基线对比\n",
    "5. **人工校正**: Active Learning 人机协作流程\n",
    "\n",
    "### 可能的进阶方向\n",
    "\n",
    "- **多波段融合**: 同时使用 ugrizy 六个波段的观测数据\n",
    "- **迁移学习**: 使用 BTSbot 预训练权重 (HuggingFace 上可获取)\n",
    "- **异常检测**: 用 Isolation Forest / Autoencoder 发现训练集中不存在的新型天体\n",
    "- **实时预警**: 接入 ZTF 实时预警流, 用你的模型做真实的天体发现\n",
    "- **可解释性**: 用 SHAP/LIME 解释模型为什么判断某个天体是超新星"
   ]
